title: FBI-agent: Mindre enn en dag på å fastslå at Russia collusion var tøv
cleaned_sentences: The FBI agent Scott Hellman explained to the court on Tuesday that it took him and a colleague less than one day to establish that the "evidence" that Clinton lawyer Michael Susman handed over to the FBI was a falsum.
Hellman said this on the first day of the trial against Susman.
